#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.atleast_3d.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.atleast\\_3d"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_3d.atleast_3d:1 of
msgid "View inputs as tensors with at least three dimensions."
msgstr "将输入视为至少具有三个维度的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_3d.atleast_3d of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_3d.atleast_3d:3
#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_3d.atleast_3d:7
#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_3d.atleast_3d:11 of
msgid ""
"One or more tensor-like sequences.  Non-tensor inputs are converted to "
"tensors.  Tensors that already have three or more dimensions are "
"preserved."
msgstr ""
"一个或多个类张量序列。非张量输入将被转换为张量。已经具有三个或更多维度的"
"张量将被保留。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_3d.atleast_3d of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_3d.atleast_3d:16 of
msgid ""
"**res1, res2, ...** -- A tensor, or list of tensors, each with ``a.ndim "
">= 3``.  Copies are avoided where possible, and views with three or more "
"dimensions are returned.  For example, a 1-D tensor of shape ``(N,)`` "
"becomes a view of shape ``(1, N, 1)``, and a 2-D tensor of shape ``(M, "
"N)`` becomes a view of shape ``(M, N, 1)``."
msgstr ""
"**res1, res2, ...** —— 一个张量，或张量列表，每个张量满足 ``a.ndim >= 3``"
"。尽可能避免复制，返回具有三个或更多维度的视图。例如，形状为 ``(N,)`` 的"
"一维张量将变成形状为 ``(1, N, 1)`` 的视图，形状为 ``(M, N)`` 的二维张量将"
"变成形状为 ``(M, N, 1)`` 的视图。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.atleast_3d.atleast_3d of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

